,488</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$470</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>24%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Ultra 2 </strong><strong>無線安全攝影機 – 雙鏡裝</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$4,288</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$3,188</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$1,100</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>26%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Essential 2 </strong><strong>室內攝影機</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$688</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$388</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$300</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>44%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Essential 2 </strong><strong>無線視訊門鈴</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$1,088</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$888</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$200</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>18%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo </strong><strong>基站，配件</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$788</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$</strong><strong>63</strong><strong>8</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$</strong><strong>15</strong><strong>0</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>19</strong><strong>%</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><h2></h2><h2><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1294484" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/02_arlopricedroppop-410x580.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="849" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/02_arlopricedroppop-410x580.jpg 410w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/02_arlopricedroppop.jpg 595w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></h2><h2>精選優惠產品詳情</h2><h2>Arlo Ultra 2 4K UHD 無線安全攝影機</h2><p>Arlo Ultra 2 具備 HDR 技術及 4K 超高清像素，並配備 180°超廣闊對角視野和彩色夜視功能，不但能夠拍攝到更廣闊的範圍捕捉更多細節，亦能在黑夜和白晝中拍下超高清影片。最多 6 個月持久電力的超大容量電池配合 IP65 防風雨設計，確保任何時候都能為你的家庭把關。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/