                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Toyota 自 1982 年推出 Camry 車系以來，全球累計銷量突破 2,100 萬輛，穩坐品牌最暢銷車款之一的殊榮。2025 年皇冠汽車正式宣佈推出搭載 Toyota 最新第五代混能系統的全新 Camry HEV，隆重登陸香港市場。新車不僅延續 Camry 的經典傳承，更通過四大革新——外觀設計、動力系統、智能配置與安全科技，為駕駛者帶來升級體驗。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294293" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_151642-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_151642-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_151642-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">全新 Camry HEV 以「動力美學」為設計核心，車身線條更流線動感，搭載全新「Hammerhead」C 字型 LED 頭燈與低重心車頭設計，搭配炙熱紅、瑰麗銅、深海藍三款全新車色及 18 寸雙色輪圈，時尚與實用兼備。動力方面，第五代混能系統結合 2.5L 引擎與電動馬達，總輸出達 230 匹馬力，0 至 100 公里加速僅需 7.2 秒，油耗低至 19.6 km/L，較前代汽油版提升 38% 燃油效率，實現性能與節能的更佳平衡。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294291" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152629-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152629-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152629-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152912-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152912-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152912-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">車廂內部同樣重新設計，配備電子影像倒後鏡、抬頭顯示器、前排冷暖通風座椅，以及後排首次加入的中央手枕控制面板，讓乘客可自行調節座椅與冷氣。三區域恆温冷氣系統與 Nanoe X 空氣淨化功能進一步提升舒適度。安全配置上，新車標配 10 個氣囊及 Toyota Safety Sense 3.0 主動安全系統，新增防護駕駛輔助功能，能提前偵測障礙物並提供轉向與制動支援，確保行車安全。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294283" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_1528180-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_1528180-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_1528180-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152754-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152754-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152754-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">娛樂體驗亦全面升級，12.3 寸觸控屏幕支援無線 Apple CarPlay，搭配 JBL 9 喇叭音響系統，為車廂增添愜意氛圍。全新 Camry HEV 售價由 HK$395,700 起（原價 HK$414,300），即日起於九龍灣、灣仔及沙田陳列室接受預訂。</span></p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294292" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152258-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152258-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152258-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br />
規格:</h3><p><b>引擎型號: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">A25A-FXS</span></p><p><b>引擎類型: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.5L 直列四缸 VVT-iE D-4S 直噴引擎</span></p><p><b>引擎馬力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">138 kW (187 PS) / 6,000 rpm</span></p><p><b>引擎扭力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">221 Nm / 3,200-5,200 rpm</span></p><p><b>電動馬達類型: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">恆久磁石同步電動馬達</span></p><p><b>電動馬達馬力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">100 kW (135 PS)</span></p><p><b>電動馬達扭力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">208 Nm</span></p><p><b>總混能系統輸出: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">169 kW (230 PS)</span></p><p><b>油耗: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">19.6 km/L</span></p><p><b>0-100 km/h 加速: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">7.2 秒</span></p><p><b>車身尺寸: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">4,920 x 1,840 x 1,455 mm</span></p><p><b>軸距: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">2,825 mm</span></p><p><strong>售價</strong>: <span style="font-weight: 400;">HK$395,700 起</span></p><br /><b>
